title.narrative: Da Nang-Quang Ngai Expressway Development Project

description.narrative: The objectives of the Project are to construct an expressway that will enhance efficiency and safety for road users traveling between Da Nang city and Quang Ngai province and build institutional capacity for expressway development in the Ministry of Transport.
